<h1>Durham Market Deliveries</h1><p>Josephine Butler College would like to announce a special partnership with Durham Indoor Markets to provide a food order service with free delivery to college.</p><p>Place your order here on Monday, Tuesday or Wednesday, and your delivery will be in the JCR Office&nbsp;on Friday morning from 10am, at which point you can pay for your delivery. You can also choose to have your order delivered to Ushaw College. A third option is to pick up your order from the Market itself.</p>